headline: Missouri American Water Rate Order Settlement Approved by Missouri Public Service Commission
summary: ST. LOUIS, May 07, 2025--The Missouri Public Service Commission (MoPSC) today approved a settlement for new water and wastewater rates for Missouri American Water.
